796
00:39:29,290 --> 00:39:30,390
I didn't kill him!

797
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:32,430
So you knew someone died.

798
00:39:33,790 --> 00:39:34,230
I...

799
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:39,430
Fine.

800
00:39:40,710 --> 00:39:41,310
I admit it.

801
00:39:42,470 --> 00:39:43,730
I came across his body.

802
00:40:36,690 --> 00:40:38,020
I took the silver ingot.

803
00:40:38,470 --> 00:40:40,180
But I really didn't kill that man.

804
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:41,170
He was lying in the bathtub.

805
00:40:41,170 --> 00:40:42,230
His hands were cold and stiff.

806
00:40:42,230 --> 00:40:43,390
He had been dead for a long time.

807
00:40:43,390 --> 00:40:44,790
You didn't kill this man.

808
00:40:44,950 --> 00:40:47,030
What about the seven lives in the neighboring county?

809
00:40:47,030 --> 00:40:47,910
Are you admitting to those?

810
00:40:47,910 --> 00:40:49,910
I haven't admitted to anything yet!

811
00:40:50,430 --> 00:40:52,400
At dawn, before daybreak,

812
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,680
that dead man's hands

813
00:40:53,900 --> 00:40:56,100
must have looked eerie and horrifying.

814
00:40:56,910 --> 00:40:58,790
If you had never killed anyone before,

815
00:40:58,790 --> 00:41:00,390
would you dare to touch them?

816
00:41:04,310 --> 00:41:07,110
You sure know how to beat around the bush, Sheriff.

817
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:07,910
Fine.

818
00:41:09,030 --> 00:41:09,670
I admit it.

819
00:41:10,470 --> 00:41:11,670
I have killed people.

820
00:41:11,790 --> 00:41:12,990
But I don't admit

821
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,320
to killing seven people.

822
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:20,130
That's way too little.

823
00:41:21,610 --> 00:41:23,140
You bunch of useless fools.

824
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:26,290
You only investigated the neighboring county.

825
00:41:26,290 --> 00:41:28,110
What about what I did

826
00:41:28,150 --> 00:41:29,480
in Shazhou and Hanzhou?

827
00:41:29,830 --> 00:41:31,030
I must have killed

828
00:41:32,350 --> 00:41:33,830
at least 20 people.
